Package org.opengrok.indexer.history

Class TagEntry

java.lang.Object
org.opengrok.indexer.history.TagEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<TagEntry>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BazaarTagEntry, BitKeeperTagEntry, MercurialTagEntry
public abstract class TagEntry extends Object implements Comparable<TagEntry>
Represents an identifier for a version control "commit" (also known as a "changeset") where the version control system uses either monotonic, linear revision numbering; or alternatively where OpenGrok uses "commit time" as a proxy for ancestry.
Author:
Stanislav Kozina
